'''Aloe Vera''' is a plant commonly used in medicinal herbalism. It is used to treat burns and skin aliments as well as healing wounds. It may look like a cactus but is related to lilies. It can grow up to 3 feet in the wild. It grows in tropical or warm climates but can be grown indoors. They need lots of sun and they do not like lots of water.

